== Preface

Through the unbounded grace of Almighty God and blessing of the greatest Apostle of God, the English version of the book of worship of the world renowned #emph[Ihya Ulum-ud-Dir] (#emph[The Revival of the Religious Sciences]) of Imam al-Ghazali, the greatest thinker of the world of Islam, the Proof of Islam, the famous Sufi and devout, has now been published in full. This book Ihya is a sea of knowleedge full of reasons and arguments, full of Quranic verses, traditions of the Holy Prophet and of the companions and the famous saints of early ages. Each subject was supported by the Quran, traditions and sayings of the learned sages and wise men and established by reasons and arguments.